Patuloy na napapabayaan ang kapakanan ng bawat Pilipino sa kada estado ng buhay. Korapsyon at Kakulangan ng Alaga at Pansin ay patuloy pa rin nangyayari kahit sino pang umupo sa pwestong kataas-taasan. 

𝙏𝙖𝙢𝙖 𝙣𝙖 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙥𝙖𝙜𝙨𝙖𝙨𝙖𝙢𝙖𝙣𝙩𝙖𝙡𝙖 — 𝙥𝙖𝙣𝙖𝙜𝙪𝙩𝙞𝙣 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙙𝙖𝙥𝙖𝙩 𝙢𝙖𝙣𝙖𝙜𝙤𝙩.

Caption by Jesthin Bhenuald Maniago 
Publication Material by Cheska Tobias

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)
⏰: 𝟲:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠 - 𝟴:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠
📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

#PATAPHFEU
